ass=\"text-right portfolio-item-info\"]\n\n<strong>Category:</strong> <a href=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/portfolio-category/graphic-design/\">Graphic design</a>, <a href=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/portfolio-category/illustration/\">illustration</a>\n<strong>Client:</strong> <a href=\"http://mccallwintersportsclub.website.siplay.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">McCall Winter Sports Club</a>\n<strong>Year:</strong> 2017\n\n[/col]\n\n[col size=\"one_half_last\"]\n\nDesigning an event poster for a ski race and aprés party? Right up my alley. When McCall Winter Sports Club contacted me to design a poster and social media advertisements for an upcoming event, I jumped at the chance.\n\n[/col]\n<h3>Modern design with a vintage flair</h3>\nMy goal for this project was to create a modern poster that feels like the vintage ski posters I love. Bringing a piece of that old-style ski flair to a contemporary audience was super fun.\n\nI chose typefaces that appear straight out of a 1930s mountain resort advertisement. The color scheme is bright yet faded. Vintage-inspired illustrations round out the composition. The poster retains a modern look by preserving the sharp edges allowed by vector graphics, and by using solid, bold color fills.\n\nMy design advertised the event in various physical locations around McCall, Idaho, as well as on social media.\n\n[caption id=\"attachment_1073\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"1200\"]<img class=\"size-full wp-image-1073\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/hometown-races/mccall-ski-poster.png\" alt=\"Hometown Races poster design\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1527\" /> <em>Poster</em>[/caption]\n\n[full_portfolio]\n\n[col size=\"one_half\"]\n\n[caption id=\"attachment_1075\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"750\"]<img class=\"size-full wp-image-1075\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/hometown-races/mccall-ski-instagram.png\" alt=\"Hometown Races Instagram post\" width=\"750\" height=\"1371\" /> <em>Instagram advertisement</em>[/caption]\n\n[/col]\n\n[col size=\"one_half_last\"]\n\n[caption id=\"attachment_1074\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"588\"]<img class=\"size-full wp-image-1074\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/hometown-races/mccall-ski-facebook.png\" alt=\"Hometown Races Facebook event post\" width=\"588\" height=\"646\" /> <em>Facebook event advertisement</em>[/caption]\n\n[/col]\n\n[/full_portfolio]','Hometown Races','','inherit','closed','closed','','1072-autosave-v1','','','2019-08-24 15:16:47','2019-08-24 22:16:47','',1072,'https://www.iamalidesign.com/2018/03/08/1072-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(51,1,'2013-07-11 21:41:46','2013-07-12 03:41:46','<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-20\" alt=\"Wine By Moonlight\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/wine_by_moonlight_ali_gray.jpg\" width=\"582\" height=\"900\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> Graphic Design\r\n<strong>Created Using:</strong> Illustrator, Photoshop\r\n<strong>Date: </strong>2011\r\n\r\nDesigned for Sapore Restaurant and Bar in Missoula, Montana for their weekly wine-tasting event.\r\n\r\nThe goal of the poster was to portray the uniqueness of this particular wine-centered event, as the room overlooks the rest of downtown Missoula from up on the 3rd story.\r\n\r\nI designed the concept, layout and graphics for the poster.','Wine by Moonlight','graphic design','inherit','open','open','','19-revision-v1','','','2013-07-11 21:41:46','2013-07-12 03:41:46','',19,'https://www.iamalidesign.com/2013/07/11/19-revision-4/',0,'revision','',0),(48,1,'2013-07-11 18:45:47','2013-07-12 00:45:47','<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-20\" alt=\"Wine By Moonlight\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/wine_by_moonlight_ali_gray.jpg\" width=\"582\" height=\"900\" />','Wine by Moonlight','Designed for Sapore Restaurant and Bar in Missoula, Montana for their weekly wine-tasting event.\r\n\r\nThe goal of t