0\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-805\" />\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2012\n\n<h2>Flora</h2>\n<img src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/flora-ali-gray.jpg\" alt=\"Flora\" width=\"500\" height=\"750\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-806\" />\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2012\n\n<h2>Dewdrops</h2>\n<img src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/dewdrops_ali_gray.jpg\" alt=\"Dewdrops\" width=\"500\" height=\"750\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-796\" />\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2012\n\n<hr>\n<p>I update this page frequently, so check back often to see my most recent photographs!</p>','Nature Photography','Collection of my photographs featuring nature themes.','inherit','open','open','','178-autosave-v1','','','2014-07-19 17:04:21','2014-07-19 23:04:21','',178,'https://www.iamalidesign.com/2013/07/13/178-autosave/',0,'revision','',0),(237,1,'2013-07-13 10:46:00','2013-07-13 16:46:00','<h2>Elemental</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-181\" alt=\"Elemental\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/elemental_ali_gray.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"750\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> Photography\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2013\r\n\r\nSpring in Yellowstone\'s Grand Canyon. Where Earth, Water, Fire and Air meet.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-182\" alt=\"Radiance of a Tree\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/radiance_of_a_tree_ali_gray.jpg\" width=\"465\" height=\"620\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> Photography\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2010\r\n\r\nTrees in autumn know how to do it right. We may try to capture they\'re beauty, and maybe sometimes we succeed, but it seems nature usually gives us the one-up.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-184\" alt=\"Where Earth Meets Sky\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/where_earth_meets_sky_ali_gray.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"387\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> Photography\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2012\r\n\r\nThe Teton Range during a dramatic sunset. I was lucky to catch this sight while on a walk up the butte near my home.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-180\" alt=\"Dewdrops\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/dewdrops_ali_gray.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"750\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> Photography\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2012\r\n\r\nGetting up for the sunrise while camping is always well worth it. In my opinion, nothing surpasses nature in the early morning.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-179\" alt=\"Barren\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/barren_ali_gray.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"750\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> Photography\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2013\r\n\r\nNatural beauty at its best.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-183\" alt=\"Reaching\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/reaching_ali_gray.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> Photography\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2009\r\n\r\nSpring moss reaching for the sun above its snow-covered log in early spring.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-185\" alt=\"Diversity\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/diversity_ali_gray.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> Photography\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2009\r\n\r\nHow many different kinds of moss and lichen can fit on one small twig?','Nature Photography','','inherit','open','open','','178-revision-v1','','','2013-07-13 10:46:00','2013-07-13 16:46:00','',178,'https://www.iamalidesign.com/2013/07/13/178-revision-3/',0,'revision','',0),(238,1,'2013-07-13 13:11:40','2013-07-13 19:11:40','<h2>Elemental</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-181\" alt=\"Elemental\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/elementa