//www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/barren_ali_gray.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"750\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> Photography\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2013\r\n\r\nNatural beauty at its best.\r\n<h2>Reaching</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-183\" alt=\"Reaching\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/reaching_ali_gray.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> Photography\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2009\r\n\r\nSpring moss reaching for the sun above its snow-covered log in early spring.\r\n<h2>Diversity</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-185\" alt=\"Diversity\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/diversity_ali_gray.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> Photography\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2009\r\n\r\nHow many different kinds of moss and lichen can fit on one small twig?','Nature Photography','','inherit','open','open','','178-revision-v1','','','2013-07-13 13:11:40','2013-07-13 19:11:40','',178,'https://www.iamalidesign.com/2013/07/13/178-revision-4/',0,'revision','',0),(291,1,'2013-07-12 10:15:57','2013-07-12 16:15:57','*I claim no rights to any of the designs on this page. All designs and content belong to <a href=\"http://www.circ.biz/\" target=\"_blank\">Circ</a>.\r\n<h2>Existing Site Mobile Re-Flow</h2>\r\n[one_half]\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-433\" alt=\"Circ About iPhone 1, web design\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/circ-about-iphone-p.jpg\" width=\"250\" height=\"519\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[one_half_last]\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-434\" alt=\"Circ About iPhone 2, web design\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/circ-about-iphone-p2.jpg\" width=\"250\" height=\"519\" />\r\n[/one_half_last]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<h2 class=\"paragraph\"><strong>Category:</strong> Web Design</h2>\r\n<strong>Created Using:</strong> Fireworks\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2012 – 2013\r\n\r\nWhen my agency\'s website was initially designed and built, mobile optimization wasn\'t really taken into consideration. Therefore I, along with my co-worker Matthew Speakman, worked to re-flow the site\'s design to fit smaller formats when needed. An example of one of the re-worked pages is above.\r\n<h2>New Page Designs</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-435\" alt=\"Circ Working With Us iPad Landscape\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/circ-working-ipad-l.jpg\" width=\"605\" height=\"465\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-436\" alt=\"Circ Working With Us iPad Portrait\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/circ-working-ipad-p.jpg\" width=\"465\" height=\"605\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-432\" alt=\"Circ 404\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/circ-404.jpg\" width=\"465\" height=\"605\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> Web Design\r\n<strong>Created Using:</strong> Fireworks\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2012 – 2013\r\n\r\nThese are the pages I designed for the website, keeping with the style already established throughout the website, yet creating their own unique identities. Copy is still being written for the Working With Us page, so it\'s not yet live.','Circ: Web Design','My design contributions to a design agency\'s website.','publish','closed','closed','','circ-web-design','','','2014-07-06 12:03:47','2014-07-06 18:03:47','',0,'https://www.iamalidesign.com/?post_type=project&#038;p=291',0,'project','',0),(294,1,'2013-07-14 16:59:38','2013-07-14 22:59:38','<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-293\" alt=\"Brew &amp; View\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/brew_and_view_ali_gray.jpg\" width=\"582\" height=\"900\" />\n\nCategory: Graphic Design\nCreated Using: Illustrator, Photoshop\nDate: 2011\n\nDesigned for Sapore Restaurant and Bar in Missoula, Montana for their weekly pizza, beer and a movie event.\n\nThis poster was used through the winter and ski season, so has a winter theme.\n\nI designed the concept, layout and graphics for the poster.','Brew & View','','inherit','open','open','','291-revision-v1','','','2013-07-14 16:59:38','2013-07-14 22:59:38','',291,'https://www.iamalidesign.com/2013/07/14/291-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(296,1,'2013-07-12 21:36:53','2013-07-13 03:36:53','<iframe src=\"http://player.vimeo.com/video/34098363?color=cdda57\" height=\"506\" width=\"900\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe>\r\n<p class=\"smaller\"><a href=\"http://vimeo.com/34098363\" target=\"_blank\">Lumiere de l\'Amour</a> from <a href=\"http://vimeo.com/aligray\" target=\"_blank\">Ali Gray</a> on <a href=\"http://vimeo.com\" target=\"_blank\">Vimeo</a>.</p>\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> Animation\r\n<strong>Created Using:</strong> Photoshop, After Effects, Cinema 4D, Wacom Tablet\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2011\r\n\r\nThis is the story of how streetlights guide two wandering robots toward each other through a surreal, ethereal world. As the main character robot sees glimpses on its screen of the other robot wandering and interacting with its own streetlights, each light compels the two to keep going and to come together.\r\n\r\nThis is my final project as a Media Arts major at the University of Montana. My partner <a href=\"http://www.wesleymeeks.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Wesley Meeks</a> and I worked on this project for about a month, from initial concepting to final render. Crunch time! We love how it turned out, though.\r\n\r\nTo see which roles I played in the project, please view the credits at the end of the animation.\r\n<h2>Initial Stylesheet</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-106\" alt=\"Lumiere Initial Stylesheet\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/lumiere_stylesheet.jpg\" width=\"900\" height=\"506\