eight=\"232\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[one_half_last]\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-358\" alt=\"Circ Brochure 4\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/circ_brochure-4.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"232\" />\r\n[/one_half_last]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> Graphic Design\r\n<strong>Created Using:</strong> InDesign\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2012 – 2013\r\n\r\nCirc wanted a version of our online portfolio that we could print out and give to prospective and current clients, or that visitors to the website could download. The brochure has more background information about each project than is available on the website, and also more projects in total. You may <a href=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/circ_brochure_web.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">download</a> the current version of the brochure to see more.\r\n<h2>Conference Room Desktop</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-361\" alt=\"Circ C Desktop Dig Deeper\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/circ_c_desktop_dig_deeper.jpg\" width=\"900\" height=\"531\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> Graphic Design\r\n<strong>Created Using:</strong> Cinema 4D\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2012\r\n\r\nI created this desktop wallpaper for the TV monitor in the Circ conference room. I wanted it to be something simplistic yet bold.\r\n<h2>Building Signage</h2>\r\n[one_half]\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-359\" alt=\"Circ Building Sign Front\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/circ_building_front_sign.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"214\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[one_half_last]\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-360\" alt=\"Circ Building Sign Back\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/circ_building_side_sign.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"214\" />\r\n[/one_half_last]\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> Graphic Design\r\n<strong>Created Using:</strong> Cinema 4D\r\