_pg1_small_900.jpg\" width=\"785\" height=\"609\" /><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-174\" alt=\"Rusalka Program 3\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Rusalka_program_pg2_small_ali_gray_900.jpg\" width=\"785\" height=\"610\" />\r\n\r\n*Note: I did not photograph the image in the video above nor do I own it or any right to it. It was simply given to me by the client to use for the videos. Also, I did not design any part of this program, nor own any rights to it.\r\n\r\nFor more information on the opera, please view this article: <a href=\"http://wire.arts.ubc.ca/events/rusalka-the-little-mermaid-story/\" target=\"_blank\">http://wire.arts.ubc.ca/events/rusalka-the-little-mermaid-story/</a> (the \"state of the art projection technology\" mentioned refers to these videos).','Rusalka','','inherit','open','open','','171-revision-v1','','','2013-07-14 19:12:54','2013-07-15 01:12:54','',171,'https://www.iamalidesign.com/2013/07/14/171-revision-4/',0,'revision','',0),(398,1,'2013-07-14 19:12:38','2013-07-15 01:12:38','<iframe src=\"http://player.vimeo.com/video/29126262?color=cdda57\" height=\"506\" width=\"900\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe>\r\n<p class=\"smaller\"><a href=\"http://vimeo.com/29126262\" target=\"_blank\">Logo Build</a> from <a href=\"http://vimeo.com/aligray\" target=\"_blank\">Ali Gray</a> on <a href=\"http://vimeo.com\" target=\"_blank\">Vimeo</a>.</p>\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> Motion Design\r\n<strong>Created Using:</strong> After Effects, Illustrator\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2011\r\n\r\nThis is a logo build I animated for one of my university After Effects classes. I didn\'t design the logo, but recreated it in Illustrator and later animated it in After Effects.\r\n\r\n*This piece has no tie to the company Clean Conscience LTD and is not approved or supported by them.','Logo Build','','inherit','open','open','','125-revision-v1','','','2013-07-14 19:12:38','2013-07-15 01:12:38','',125,'https://www.iamalidesign.com/2013/07/14/125-revision-4/',0,'revision','',0),(399,1,'2013-07-14 19:12:25','2013-07-15 01:12:25','<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-83\" alt=\"Typography Poster\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/typography_poster_ali_gray.jpg\" width=\"485\" height=\"749\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> Graphic Design\r\n<strong>Created Using:</strong> Illustrator\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2012\r\n\r\nThis is an informational poster I made for a fake event as part of a university typography class.\r\n\r\nWe could only use simple graphical elements: the main concentration was supposed to be on letterform and manipulating the layout of text on the page to create something interesting.\r\n\r\nThis piece are not tied to any of the real organizations portrayed on the posters in any way.','Typography Poster','','inherit','open','open','','82-revision-v1','','','2013-07-14 19:12:25','2013-07-15 01:12:25','',82,'https://www.iamalidesign.com/2013/07/14/82-revision-5/',0,'revision','',0),(400,1,'2013-07-16 13:49:52','2013-07-16 19:49:52','<h2>Drip, Drip, Drip</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-202\" alt=\"Drip Drip Drip\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/drip_drip_drip_ali_gray.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> Photography\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2009\r\n\r\nI took this photo as part of a photography assignment for a university class, in which we had to find or create interesting text and letterforms and photograph them. I created and lit this scene in order to accomplish the look and concept I was after.\r\n<h2>China Shipping</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-200\" alt=\"China Shipping\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/china_shipping_ali_gray.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"574\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> Photography\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2012\r\n\r\nWhile out scouting for interesting typography and text to photograph for a typography class, I suddenly happened upon this fantastic truck parked in a downtown Missoula parking lot. What a great find!\r\n<h2>The Color of Rust</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-205\" alt=\"The Color of Rust\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/the_color_of_rust_ali_gray.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"667\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> Photography\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2012\r\n\r\nIt\'s amazing what you can find among a bunch of old rusty mining equipment in the middle of an old field in the industrial sector of a Montana town.\r\n<h2>Million Dollar</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-203\" alt=\"Million Dollar\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/million_dollar_ali_gray.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"750\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> Photography\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2012\r\n\r\nAs I currently live in Jackson Hole, WY, I figured I might as well take a picture of the famous bar every one of the thousands of tourists take pictures of every day—but in a different way.\r\n<h2>Doble V</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-201\" alt=\"Doble V\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/doble_v_ali_gray.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"667\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> Photography\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2012\r\n\r\nFinding the right crop is what turning a boring apartment complex sign into something unique is all about.\r\n<h2>Symmetry</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-204\" alt=\"Symmetry\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/symmetry_ali_gray.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"629\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> Photography\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2012\r\n\r\nAnother interesting find for my typography photography assignment. Loved the symmetrical and asymmetrical aspects of the inside of this gazebo roof.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Text Photography','Collection of my photographs featuring text & typography  themes.','inherit','open','open','','199-revision-v1','','','2013-07-16 13:49:52','2013-07-16 19:49:52','',199,'https://www.iamalidesign.com/2013/07/16/199-revision-6/',0,'revision','',0),(401,1,'2013-07-14 19:12:15','2013-07-15 01:12:15','<h2>Elemental</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-181\" alt=\"Elemental\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/elemental_ali_gray.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"750\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> Photography\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2013\r\n\r\nSpring in Yellowstone\'s Grand Canyon. Where Earth, Water, Fire and Air meet.\r\n<h2>Edge</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-225\" alt=\"Edge\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/edge_ali_gray.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"750\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> Photography\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2013\r\n\r\nAt the Sulfur Pot in Yellowstone, stench doesn\'t effect beauty.\r\n<h2>Radiance of a Tree</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-182\" alt=\"Radiance of a Tree\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/radiance_of_a_tree_ali_gray.jpg\" width=\"465\" height=\"620\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> Photography\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2010\r\n\r\nTrees in autumn know how to do it right. We may try to capture they\'re beauty, and maybe sometimes we succeed, but it seems nature usually gives us the one-up.\r\n<h2>Where Earth Meets Sky</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-184\" alt=\"Where Earth Meets Sky\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/where_earth_meets_sky_ali_gray.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"387\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> Photography\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2012\r\n\r\nThe Teton Range during a dramatic sunset. I was lucky to catch this sight while on a walk up the butte near my home.\r\n<h2>Dewdrops</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-180\" alt=\"Dewdrops\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/dewdrops_ali_gray.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"750\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> Photography\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2012\r\n\r\nGetting up for the sunrise while camping is always well worth it. In my opinion, nothing surpasses nature in the early morning.\r\n<h2>Barren</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-179\" alt=\"Barren\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/barren_ali_gray.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"750\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> Photography\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2013\r\n\r\nNatural beauty at its best.\r\n<h2>Reaching</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-183\" alt=\"Reaching\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/reaching_ali_gray.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> Photography\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2009\r\n\r\nSpring moss reaching for the sun above its snow-covered log in early spring.\r\n<h2>Diversity</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-185\" alt=\"Diversity\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/diversity_ali_gray.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> Photography\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2009\r\n\r\nHow many different kinds of moss and lichen can fit on one small twig?','Nature Photography','','inherit','open','open','','178-revision-v1','','','2013-07-14 19:12:15','2013-07-15 01:12:15','',178,'https://www.iamalidesign.com/2013/07/14/178-revision-8/',0,'revision','',0),(402,1,'2013-07-14 19:12:03','2013-07-15 01:12:03','<iframe src=\"http://player.vimeo.com/video/15852498?color=cdda57\" height=\"471\" width=\"856\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe>\r\n<p class=\"smaller\"><a href=\"http://vimeo.com/15852498\" target=\"_blank\">A Simple Gift</a> from <a href=\"http://vimeo.com/aligray\" target=\"_blank\">Ali Gray</a> on <a 