n.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/showcase-homes.jpg\" width=\"900\" height=\"558\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> Web Design\r\n<strong>Created Using:</strong> WordPress, Photoshop\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2013\r\n\r\nThis is the <a href=\"http://homesteadmag.com/jackson-hole-showcase-of-homes/\" target=\"_blank\">Showcase of Homes page</a> of the <a href=\"http://homesteadmag.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Homestead Magazine website</a>. I manipulated a WordPress theme to create the entire website. I claim no rights whatsoever: the website and all content belong to Homestead Magazine and the respective photographers.','Jackson Hole Showcase of Homes','Logo and print materials for the 2013 Jackson Hole Showcase of Homes.','inherit','open','open','','222-revision-v1','','','2013-07-16 20:21:32','2013-07-17 02:21:32','',222,'https://www.iamalidesign.com/2013/07/16/222-revision-11/',0,'revision','',0),(408,1,'2013-07-16 15:51:51','2013-07-16 21:51:51','<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-293\" alt=\"Brew &amp; View\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/brew_and_view_ali_gray.jpg\" width=\"582\" height=\"900\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> Graphic Design\r\n<strong>Created Using:</strong> Illustrator, Photoshop\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2011\r\n\r\nDesigned for Sapore Restaurant &amp; Bar in Missoula, Montana for their weekly pizza, beer and a movie event.\r\n\r\nThis poster was used through the winter and ski season, so has a winter theme.\r\n\r\nI designed the concept, layout and graphics for the poster.','Brew & View','An event poster created for a restaurant in Missoula, MT.','inherit','open','open','','291-revision-v1','','','2013-07-16 15:51:51','2013-07-16 21:51:51','',291,'https://www.iamalidesign.com/2013/07/16/291-revision-6/',0,'revision','',0),(409,1,'2013-07-14 19:11:21','2013-07-15 01:11:21','<iframe src=\"http://player.vimeo.com/video/16623351?color=cdda57\" height=\"491\" width=\"872\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe>\r\n<p class=\"smaller\"><a href=\"http://vimeo.com/16623351\" target=\"_blank\">Overgrown</a> from <a href=\"http://vimeo.com/aligray\" target=\"_blank\">Ali Gray</a> on <a href=\"http://vimeo.com\" target=\"_blank\">Vimeo</a>.</p>\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> Animation\r\n<strong>Created Using:</strong> Paper, Chair, Lamp, Photoshop, Final Cut, Logic\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2011\r\n\r\nThis is an experimental stop motion animation I did for my University of Montana Media Arts animation class.\r\n\r\nIt consists of dozens of little creepy tree paper cutouts that I taped to a chair, lit with a lamp, and then photographed the shadows. I used a replacement animation technique. I made the title by cutting out the words from a piece of paper, holding it up to a light, taking the picture, then inverting the black and white.\r\n\r\nI wanted to experiment with different shadows to create a unique, abstract stop motion animation. The soundtrack is a custom sound design piece I created in Logic.\r\n<h2>Trees</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-119\" alt=\"Overgrown Trees\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/overgrown_trees.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"750\" />\r\n<h2>Storyboards</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-117\" alt=\"Overgrown Storyboards\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/overgrown_storyboards.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"673\" />\r\n<h2>Tree &amp; Animation Setup Concepts</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-118\" alt=\"Overgrown Tree Concepts\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/overgrown_tree_concepts.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" />','Overgrown','','inherit','open','open','','116-revision-v1','','','2013-07-14 19:11:21','2013-07-15 01:11:21','',116,'https://www.iamalidesign.com/2013/07/14/116-revision-4/',0,'revision','',0),(410,1,'2013-07-14 19:11:10','2013-07-15 01:11:10','<h2>Orange</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignn