, Photoshop\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2012\r\n\r\nTypogram: a word that, through the manipulation of the letterform itself, illustrates the meaning of the word.\r\n\r\nThis is a series of typograms I designed and created for a university typography class. I also included my pencil and paper concept sketches.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-64\" style=\"float: left;\" alt=\"Typogram Sketches 1\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/typogram_sketches1.jpg\" width=\"50%\" /><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-65\" style=\"float: left;\" alt=\"Typogram Sketches 2\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/typogram_sketches2.jpg\" width=\"50%\" />','Typograms','A series of typography pieces which illustrate the meaning of a word using the word itself.','inherit','open','open','','58-revision-v1','','','2013-07-16 13:52:57','2013-07-16 19:52:57','',58,'https://www.iamalidesign.com/2013/07/16/58-revision-8/',0,'revision','',0),(479,1,'2013-07-17 12:51:30','2013-07-17 18:51:30','<h2>Logo Concepts</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-419\" alt=\"Showcase of Homes Logo\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/soh-logo.jpg\" width=\"900\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> Graphic Design\r\n<strong>Created Using:</strong> Illustrator\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2013\r\n\r\nThese are some of the concepts I designed for the brand new <a href=\"http://homesteadmag.com/jackson-hole-showcase-of-homes/\" target=\"_blank\">Jackson Hole Showcase of Homes</a>. I wanted to represent the homes themselves in this logo: modern yet elegant, built from materials of the forests and mountains.\r\n<h2>Information Pamphlet</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-417\" alt=\"Showcase of Homes Information 1\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/soh_take-away-1.jpg\" width=\"465\" height=\"602\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-imag