eated Using:</strong> InDesign\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2012 – 2013\r\n\r\nCirc wanted a version of our online portfolio that we could print out and give to prospective and current clients, or that visitors to the website could download. The brochure has more background information about each project than is available on the website, and also more projects in total. You may <a href=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/circ_brochure_web.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">download</a> the current version of the brochure to see more.\r\n<h2>Conference Room Desktop</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-361\" alt=\"Circ C Desktop Dig Deeper\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/circ_c_desktop_dig_deeper.jpg\" width=\"900\" height=\"531\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> Graphic Design\r\n<strong>Created Using:</strong> Cinema 4D\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2012\r\n\r\nI created this desktop wallpaper for the TV monitor in the Circ conference room. I wanted it to be something simplistic yet bold.\r\n<h2>Building Signage</h2>\r\n[one_half]\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-359\" alt=\"Circ Building Sign Front\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/circ_building_front_sign.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"214\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[one_half_last]\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-360\" alt=\"Circ Building Sign Back\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/circ_building_side_sign.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"214\" />\r\n[/one_half_last]\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> Graphic Design\r\n<strong>Created Using:</strong> Cinema 4D\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2012 – 2013\r\n\r\n3D mockups I created to demonstrate what the updated signage will look like on the Circ office exterior.','Circ: Graphic Design','Features business collateral, advertising material pieces, a desktop wallpaper, and exterior signage mockups for Circ, in Jackson, WY.','inherit','open','open','','353-revision-v1','','','2013-08-03 21:39:12','2013-08-04 03:39:12','',353,'https://www.iamalidesign.com/2013/08/03/353-revision-17/',0,'revision','',0),(550,1,'2013-07-28 17:15:22','2013-07-28 23:15:22','*I claim no rights to any of the designs on this page. All designs and content belong to <a href=\"http://www.circ.biz/\" target=\"_blank\">Circ</a>.\r\n<h2>Existing Site Mobile Re-Flow</h2>\r\n[one_half]\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-433\" alt=\"Circ About iPhone 1\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/circ-about-iphone-p.jpg\" width=\"250\" height=\"519\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[one_half_last]\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-434\" alt=\"Circ About iPhone 2\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/circ-about-iphone-p2.jpg\" width=\"250\" height=\"519\" />\r\n[/one_half_last]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> Web Design\r\n<strong>Created Using:</strong> Fireworks\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2012 – 2013\r\n\r\nWhen my agency\'s website was initially designed and built, mobile optimization wasn\'t really taken into consideration. Therefore I, along with my co-worker Matthew Speakman, worked to re-flow the site\'s design to fit smaller formats when needed. An example of one of the re-worked pages is above.\r\n<h2>New Page Designs</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-435\" alt=\"Circ Working With Us iPad Landscape\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/circ-working-ipad-l.jpg\" width=\"605\" height=\"465\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-436\" alt=\"Circ Working With Us iPad Portrait\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/circ-working-ipad-p.jpg\" width=\"465\" height=\"605\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-432\" alt=\"Circ 404\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/circ-404.jpg\" width=\"465\" height=\"605\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> Web Design\r\n<strong>Created Using:</strong> Fireworks\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2012 – 2013\r\n\r\nThese are the pages I designed for the website, keeping with the style already established throughout the website, yet creating their own unique identities. Copy is still being written for the Working With Us page, so it\'s not yet live.','Circ: Web Design','My design contributions to my agency\'s website.','inherit','open','open','','291-revision-v1','','','2013-07-28 17:15:22','2013-07-28 23:15:22','',291,'https://www.iamalidesign.com/2013/07/28/291-revision-28/',0,'revision','',0),(551,1,'2013-07-29 23:33:55','2013-07-30 05:33:55','*The designs on this page belong to the <a href=\"http://www.umt.edu/\" target=\"_blank\">University of Montana</a> and <a href=\"http://www.cas.umt.edu/sfdesigns/\" target=\"_blank\">Spectral Fusion Designs</a>.\r\n<h2>UM Environmental Studies</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-506\" alt=\"Environmental Studies Website\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/evst-ali_gray.jpg\" width=\"900\" height=\"574\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> Web Design / Graphic Design\r\n<strong>Created Using:</strong> Fireworks, Illustrator, Dreamweaver\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2011\r\n\r\nThis is a website I designed and developed for the University of Montana Environmental Studies program. I also designed the Environmental Studies logo and header graphic.\r\n\r\nThe current website has strayed quite a bit from my <a href=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/evst.jpg\" target=\"_blank\">original design</a> under EVST\'s management, but you can still view it live at <a href=\"http://www.cas.umt.edu/evst/\" target=\"_blank\">www.cas.umt.edu/evst</a>.\r\n<h2>UM Geosciences</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-514\" alt=\"UM Geosciences Website\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/geosciences-ali_gray.jpg\" width=\"900\" height=\"574\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> Web Design / Graphic Design\r\n<strong>Created Using:</strong> Fireworks, Illustrator, Dreamweaver, Cascade CMS\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2012\r\n\r\nI designed and developed this website for the University of Montana Department of Geosciences. I had planned on implementing a JQuery slideshow on the homepage, but the Geosciences faculty and staff chose to continue using Picasa. I also designed the footer mountain graphic and EBL, River Center, IFG, and Newsletter icons for the site.\r\n\r\nYou can view the site live at <a href=\"http://www.cas.umt.edu/geosciences/\" target=\"_blank\">www.cas.umt.edu/geosciences</a>, or view the <a href=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/geosciences_ali_gray.jpg\" target=\"_blank\">full design</a>.\r\n<h2>UM CBSD</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-518\" alt=\"UM CBSD Website\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/cbsd-ali_gray.jpg\" width=\"900\" height=\"574\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> Web Design\r\n<strong>Created Using:</strong> Fireworks, Dreamweaver, Cascade CMS\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2012\r\n\r\nThis is a website I designed and developed for The University of Montana Center for Biomolecular Structure and Dynamics (CBSD).\r\n\r\nYou can view the site live at <a href=\"http://cas.umt.edu/departments/cbsd/\" target=\"_blank\">www.cas.umt.edu/departments/cbsd</a>.\r\n<h2>UM Irish Studies</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-520\" alt=\"UM Irish Studies Website Design\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/irish-studies-ipad-ali-gray.jpg\" width=\"465\" height=\"605\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> Web Design\r\n<strong>Created Using:</strong> Fireworks\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2012\r\n\r\nUnfortunately, another design was ultimately chosen, but this was my design for the UM Irish Studies program. I also designed this Irish Studies logo. This design isn\'t associated with UM Irish Studies in any way.\r\n<h2>West Slope Trout Unlimited</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-524\" alt=\"West Slope Trout Unlimited\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/tu-west-slope-ali-gray.jpg\" width=\"605\" height=\"465\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> Web Design\r\n<strong>Created Using:</strong> Fireworks\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2012\r\n\r\nAlthough this isn\'t a university website design, I did create it while working as a student web designer at Spectral Fusion Designs. We sometimes designed sites for local non-profits, and this is one example. Another design was ultimately chosen, but I feel this is a good design to showcase here anyway.\r\n\r\n*No part of this design is associated with Trout Unlimited West Slope in any way. All the images are placeholders, and I don\'t claim ownership or own rights to any of the photos.','University Website Designs','Collection of websites I designed and developed for The University of Montana as a student web design worker.','inherit','open','open','','162-revision-v1','','','2013-07-29 23:33:55','2013-07-30 05:33:55','',162,'https://www.iamalidesign.com/2013/07/29/162-revision-22/',0,'revision','',0),(604,1,'2013-07-12 01:29:39','2013-07-12 07:29:39','[alpine-phototile-for-instagram id=946 user=\"alirgray\" src=\"user_recent\" imgl=\"instagram\" style=\"cascade\" col=\"2\" size=\"L\" num=\"30\" align=\"center\" max=\"100%\" nocredit=\"1\"]\r\n\r\nView all my <a href=\"http://instagram.com/alirgray\" target=\"_blank\">Instagram photography</a>.\r\n\r\n<hr>\r\n<p>I update this page frequently, so check back often to see my most recent photographs!</p>','Instagram Photography','Collection of my photographs from Instagram.','publish','closed','closed','','instagram-photography','','','2014-07-06 13:50:03','2014-07-06 19:50:03','',0,'https://www.iamalidesign.com/?post_type=project&#038;p=604',0,'project','',0),(605,1,'2014-06-13 17:27:39','2014-06-13 23:27:39','','Instagram Ph