the Missoula area. Due to certain circumstances, I couldn\'t see the website through to completion. I do however still like the initial design I\'d done, although she has asked to remain anonymous. Her logo would appear in the blank white circle in the design.\r\n\r\nThe goal of this design was to create a somewhat rustic yet still professional website that added to the photographer\'s style rather than distracted from it, and also to convey her style in a way that a plain white, contemporary design couldn\'t.','Freelance Websites','A collection of some of my freelance web design projects.','inherit','open','open','','158-revision-v1','','','2014-07-06 11:58:39','2014-07-06 17:58:39','',158,'https://www.iamalidesign.com/2014/07/06/158-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(642,1,'2014-07-06 12:01:44','2014-07-06 18:01:44','*I claim no rights to any of the designs on this page. All designs and content belong to <a href=\"http://www.circ.biz/\" target=\"_blank\">Circ</a>.\r\n<h2>Existing Site Mobile Re-Flow</h2>\r\n[one_half]\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-433\" alt=\"Circ About iPhone 1, web design\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/circ-about-iphone-p.jpg\" width=\"250\" height=\"519\" />\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[one_half_last]\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-434\" alt=\"Circ About iPhone 2, web design\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/circ-about-iphone-p2.jpg\" width=\"250\" height=\"519\" />\r\n[/one_half_last]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<h2 class=\"paragraph\"><strong>Category:</strong> Web Design</h2>\r\n<strong>Created Using:</strong> Fireworks\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2012 – 2013\r\n\r\nWhen my agency\'s website was initially designed and built, mobile optimization wasn\'t really taken into consideration. Therefore I, along with my co-worker Matthew Speakman, worked to re-flow the site\'s design to fit smaller formats when needed. An example of one of the re-worked pages is above.\r\n<h2>New Page Designs</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-435\" alt=\"Circ Working With Us iPad Landscape\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/circ-working-ipad-l.jpg\" width=\"605\" height=\"465\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-436\" alt=\"Circ Working With Us iPad Portrait\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/circ-working-ipad-p.jpg\" width=\"465\" height=\"605\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-432\" alt=\"Circ 404\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/circ-404.jpg\" width=\"465\" height=\"605\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> Web Design\r\n<strong>Created Using:</strong> Fireworks\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2012 – 2013\r\n\r\nThese are the pages I designed for the website, keeping with the style already established throughout the website, yet creating their own unique identities. Copy is still being written for the Working With Us page, so it\'s not yet live.','Circ: Web Design','My design contributions to a design agency\'s website.','inherit','open','open','','291-revision-v1','','','2014-07-06 12:01:44','2014-07-06 18:01:44','',291,'https://www.iamalidesign.com/2014/07/06/291-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(643,1,'2014-07-06 12:07:49','2014-07-06 18:07:49','<h2 class=\"firstH1\">Teeth</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-214\" alt=\"Teeth, photography\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/teeth_ali_gray.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"750\" />\r\n\r\n<h2 class=\"paragraph\"><strong>Category:</strong> Photography</h2>\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2011\r\n\r\nI took this photo at my parents\' house. There is an awesome vintage saw hanging on the side of the log garage, and I couldn\'t resist photographing its gnarly teeth and their sharp contrast against the circular tree rings.\r\n<h2>Oxidized</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-211\" alt=\"Oxidized\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/oxidized_ali_gray.jpg\" width=\"465\" height=\"620\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> Photography\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2009\r\n\r\nI took this photo at Flathead Lake in Montana. An old, rusty and weathered boat shack on the shore was absolutely perfect for a photo.\r\n<h2>Winter Cycle</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-215\" alt=\"Winter Cycle\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/winter_cycle_ali_gray.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> Photography\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2011\r\n\r\nPart of the rope tow at the top of Lost Trail Powder Mountain ski area in Montana/Idaho. Loved the orange.\r\n<h2>225</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224\" alt=\"Doorway\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/doorway_ali_gray.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"750\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> Photography\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2013\r\n\r\nAmazing door to one of the rooms at the Old Faithful Inn in Yellowstone.\r\n<h2>Sail Away</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-213\" alt=\"Sail Away\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/sail_away_ali_gray.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"750\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> Photography\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2012\r\n\r\nTaken while sailing on Jackson Lake in Grand Teton National Park. Went a little overboard with Photoshop, but I think the abstract-ness of the photo called for it.\r\n<h2>Color Wheel</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-208\" alt=\"Color Wheel\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/circular_color_ali_gray.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> Photography\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2010\r\n\r\nThis crayon tower had such amazing colors! Boosting said colors beyond the natural is always fun, as well.\r\n<h2>Nature\'s Symmetry</h2>\r\