get=\"_blank\">Ali Gray</a> on <a href=\"http://vimeo.com\" target=\"_blank\">Vimeo</a>.</p>\r\n<h2 class=\"paragraph\"><strong>Category:</strong> Animation / Motion Design</h2>\r\n<strong>Created Using:</strong> Photoshop, Illustrator, After Effects, Logic\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2011\r\n\r\nThis is a fake title sequence I designed and animated for an After Effects class. The only real person credited in the title sequence is me, and I made up the film and film name, as well.\r\n\r\nIn creating this piece, I was going for something fun, colorful, jazzy, and full of animation.\r\n\r\nThe music is \"Rythme Gitan\" by Latché Swing <a href=\"http://www.jamendo.com/en\" target=\"_blank\">(jamendo.com/en/artist/latche_swing_(3))</a>.\r\n<h2>Storyboards</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-123\" alt=\"Title Sequence Storyboards, motion design\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/title_sequence_storyboards.jpg\" width=\"900\" height=\"334\" />','Title Sequence','Title sequence for a fictional film which features geometric shapes, fun colors and jazzy music.','inherit','open','open','','122-revision-v1','','','2014-07-06 12:12:22','2014-07-06 18:12:22','',122,'https://www.iamalidesign.com/2014/07/06/122-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(646,1,'2014-07-06 12:17:00','2014-07-06 18:17:00','<iframe src=\"http://player.vimeo.com/video/32268385?color=cdda57\" height=\"506\" width=\"900\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe>\r\n<p class=\"smaller\"><a href=\"http://vimeo.com/32268385\" target=\"_blank\">Title Sequence</a> from <a href=\"http://vimeo.com/aligray\" target=\"_blank\">Ali Gray</a> on <a href=\"http://vimeo.com\" target=\"_blank\">Vimeo</a>.</p>\r\n<h2 class=\"paragraph\"><strong>Category:</strong> Animation / Motion Design</h2>\r\n<strong>Created Using:</strong> Photoshop, Illustrator, After Effects, Logic\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2011\r\n\r\nGetting into motion design and animation in college, I wanted to create a title sequence from the start. With this piece for an After Effects class, I finally had the opportunity! Although at the time I didn\'t have a friend shooting a film and I find recreating things that have already been done a bit cliche (aka for a Hollywood movie), a fake title sequence was in order. The film in this animation is imaginary, and the only real person credited is me.\r\n\r\nIn creating this piece, I was going for something fun, colorful, jazzy, and full of high-energy animation.\r\n\r\nThe music is \"Rythme Gitan\" by Latché Swing <a href=\"http://www.jamendo.com/en\" target=\"_blank\">(jamendo.com/en/artist/latche_swing_(3))</a>.\r\n<h2>Storyboards</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-123\" alt=\"Title Sequence Storyboards, motion design\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/title_sequence_storyboards.jpg\" width=\"900\" height=\"334\" />','Title Sequence','Title sequence for a fictional film which features geometric shapes, fun colors and jazzy music.','inherit','open','open','','122-revision-v1','','','2014-07-06 12:17:00','2014-07-06 18:17:00','',122,'https://www.iamalidesign.com/2014/07/06/122-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(647,1,'2014-07-06 12:31:13','2014-07-06 18:31:13','<h2 class=\"firstH1\">Perspective View 1</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-154\" alt=\"Steampunk Goggles 1, 3D\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/steampunk_goggles_persp_ali_gray.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"571\" />\r\n<h2>Perspective View 2</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-155\" alt=\"Steampunk Goggles 2\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/steampunk_goggles_persp3_ali_gray.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"571\" />\r\n<h2>Front View</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-153\" alt=\"Steampunk Goggles 3\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/steampunk_goggles_front_ali_gray.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"571\" />\