b&q=million%20dollar%20cowboy%20bar%20sign&revid=1985559828&rls=org.mozilla%3Aen-US%3Aofficial&tbm=isch&imgdii=_\" target=\"_blank\">famous bar</a> every one of the thousands of tourists take pictures of every day—but in a different way.\n\n<h2>Hawthorne 44</h2>\n<img src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/hawthorne-44-ali-gray.jpg\" alt=\"Hawthorne 44\" width=\"500\" height=\"750\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-756\" />\n\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2014\n\nThere\'s a condo building down the street from my apartment with some really cool typography.\n\n<h2>Vintage</h2>\n<img src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/vintage-ali-gray.jpg\" alt=\"Vintage\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-757\" />\n\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2014\nThere are some really great old signs and building fa\n\n<h2>China Shipping</h2>\n<img src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/china_shipping_ali_gray.jpg\" alt=\"China Shipping, photography\" width=\"800\" height=\"574\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-750\" />\n\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2012\n\nWhile out scouting for interesting typography and text to photograph for a typography class, I suddenly happened upon this fantastic truck parked in a downtown Missoula parking lot. What a great find!\n\n<h2>Doble V</h2>\n<img src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/doble_v_ali_gray.jpg\" alt=\"Doble V\" width=\"500\" height=\"667\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-753\" />\n\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2012\n\nFinding the right crop is what turning a boring apartment complex sign into something unique is all about.\n<h2>Symmetry</h2>\n<img src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/symmetry_ali_gray.jpg\" alt=\"Symmetry\" width=\"800\" height=\"629\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-754\" />\n\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2012\n\nAnother interesting find for my typography photography assignment. Loved the symmetrical and asymmetrical aspects of the inside of this gazebo roof.\n\n<h2>225</h2>\n<img src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/doorway_ali_gray.jpg\" alt=\"Doorway\" width=\"500\" height=\"750\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-710\" />\n\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2013\n\nAmazing door to one of the rooms at the Old Faithful Inn in Yellowstone.\n\n<hr>\n<p>I update this page frequently, so check back often to see my most recent photographs!</p>','Text Photography','Collection of my photographs featuring text & typography themes.','inherit','open','open','','199-autosave-v1','','','2014-07-07 20:42:09','2014-07-08 02:42:09','',199,'https://www.iamalidesign.com/2014/07/06/199-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(653,1,'2014-07-06 12:41:06','2014-07-06 18:41:06','<h2 class=\"firstH1\">Drip, Drip, Drip</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-202\" alt=\"Drip Drip Drip, photography\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/drip_drip_drip_ali_gray.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<h2 class=\"paragraph\"><strong>Category:</strong> Photography</h2>\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2009\r\n\r\nI took this photo as part of a photography assignment for a university class, in which we had to find or create interesting text and letterforms and photograph them. I created and lit this scene in order to accomplish the look and concept I was after.\r\n<h2>China Shipping</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-200\" alt=\"China Shipping\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/china_shipping_ali_gray.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"574\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> Photography\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2012\r\n\r\nWhile out scouting for interesting typography and text to photograph for a typography class, I suddenly happened upon this fantastic truck parked in a downtown Missoula parking lot. What a great find!\r\n<h2>The Color of Rust</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-imag