'<h2 class=\"firstH1\">Rusalka: The Little Mermaid Story – Set Backdrop Motion Design Videos</h2>\r\nThis is one of 16 videos I made for the University of British Columbia\'s production of Antonín Dvorák\'s opera Rusalka: The Little Mermaid Story, February 9-12, 2012. The videos were projected onto the back of the set behind the stage. I made them in After Effects, using various effects and particles.\r\n\r\nHere\'s one of the videos, shortened a bit:\r\n<iframe src=\"http://player.vimeo.com/video/38334568?color=c9ff23\" height=\"675\" width=\"900\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://vimeo.com/38334568\">Rusalka Opera, University of British Colombia, Set Projection Video</a> from <a href=\"http://vimeo.com/aligray\">Ali Gray</a> on <a href=\"https://vimeo.com\">Vimeo</a>.\r\n<h2 class=\"paragraph\"><strong>Categories:</strong> Motion Design</h2>\r\n<strong>Created Using:</strong> Photoshop, After Effects\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2012\r\n\r\nHere\'s the program (which I didn\'t design, but am credited as \"Ali Gray: Motion Graphic Artist\"):\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-172\" alt=\"Rusalka Program 1, motion design\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Rusalka_program_cover_small.jpg\" width=\"388\" height=\"613\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-173\" alt=\"Ruslaka Program 2\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Rusalka_program_pg1_small_900.jpg\" width=\"785\" height=\"609\" /><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-174\" alt=\"Rusalka Program 3\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Rusalka_program_pg2_small_ali_gray_900.jpg\" width=\"785\" height=\"610\" />\r\n\r\n*Note: I did not photograph the image in the video above nor do I own it or any right to it. It was simply given to me by the client to use for the videos. Also, I did not design any part of this program, nor own any rights to it.\r\n\r\nFor more information on the opera, please view this article: <a href=\"http://wire.arts.ubc.ca/events/rusalka-the-little-mermaid-story/\" target=\"_blank\">http://wire.arts.ubc.ca/events/rusalka-the-little-mermaid-story/</a> (the \"state of the art projection technology\" mentioned refers to these videos).','Rusalka','Videos created for the backdrop of an opera put on by the University of British Colombia.','inherit','open','open','','171-revision-v1','','','2014-07-06 13:21:27','2014-07-06 19:21:27','',171,'https://www.iamalidesign.com/2014/07/06/171-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(667,1,'2014-07-06 13:26:32','2014-07-06 19:26:32','<iframe src=\"http://player.vimeo.com/video/29126262?color=cdda57\" height=\"506\" width=\"900\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe>\r\n<p class=\"smaller\"><a href=\"http://vimeo.com/29126262\" target=\"_blank\">Logo Build</a> from <a href=\"http://vimeo.com/aligray\" target=\"_blank\">Ali Gray</a> on <a href=\"http://vimeo.com\" target=\"_blank\">Vimeo</a>.</p>\r\n<h2 class=\"paragraph\"><strong>Category:</strong> Motion Design</h2>\r\n<strong>Created Using:</strong> After Effects, Illustrator\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2011\r\n\r\nThis is a logo build I animated for one of my university After Effects classes. I didn\'t design the logo, but recreated it in Illustrator and later animated it in After Effects. In the animation, I wanted to convey the natural quality of the product, both in the animation itself (clean, smooth, growing, light) and the sound design (birds).\r\n\r\n*This piece has no tie to the company Clean Conscience LTD and is not approved or supported by them.','Logo Build','Six-second animated logo.','inherit','open','open','','125-revision-v1','','','2014-07-06 13:26:32','2014-07-06 19:26:32','',125,'https://www.iamalidesign.com/2014/07/06/125-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(668,1,'2014-07-06 13:27:20','2014-07-06 19:27:20','<iframe src=\"http://player.vimeo.com/video/29126262?color=cdda57\" height=\"506\" width=\"9