ploads/2013/07/china_shipping_ali_gray.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"574\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2012\r\n\r\nWhile out scouting for interesting typography and text to photograph for a typography class, I suddenly happened upon this fantastic truck parked in a downtown Missoula parking lot. What a great find!\r\n<h2>The Color of Rust</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-205\" alt=\"The Color of Rust\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/the_color_of_rust_ali_gray.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"667\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2012\r\n\r\nIt\'s amazing what you can find among a bunch of old rusty mining equipment in the middle of an old field in the industrial sector of a Montana town.\r\n<h2>Million Dollar</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-203\" alt=\"Million Dollar\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/million_dollar_ali_gray.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"750\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2012\r\n\r\nAs I currently live in Jackson Hole, WY, I figured I might as well take a picture of the <a href=\"https://www.google.com/search?q=million+dollar+cowboy+bar&client=firefox-a&hs=eoD&rls=org.mozilla:en-US:official&channel=sb&source=lnms&tbm=isch&sa=X&ei=eZi5U8HTDM-myASIqYCwBg&ved=0CAoQ_AUoAw&biw=1540&bih=758#channel=sb&q=million%20dollar%20cowboy%20bar%20sign&revid=1985559828&rls=org.mozilla%3Aen-US%3Aofficial&tbm=isch&imgdii=_\" target=\"_blank\">famous bar</a> every one of the thousands of tourists take pictures of every day—but in a different way.\r\n<h2>Doble V</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-201\" alt=\"Doble V\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/doble_v_ali_gray.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"667\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2012\r\n\r\nFinding the right crop is what turning a boring apartment complex sign into something unique is all about.\r\n<h2>Symmetry</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-204\" alt=\"Symmetry\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/symmetry_ali_gray.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"629\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2012\r\n\r\nAnother interesting find for my typography photography assignment. Loved the symmetrical and asymmetrical aspects of the inside of this gazebo roof.\r\n\r\n<hr>\r\n<p>I update this page frequently, so check back often to see my most recent photographs!</p>','Text Photography','Collection of my photographs featuring text & typography themes.','inherit','open','open','','199-revision-v1','','','2014-07-06 13:47:22','2014-07-06 19:47:22','',199,'https://www.iamalidesign.com/2014/07/06/199-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(669,1,'2014-07-06 13:35:23','2014-07-06 19:35:23','<h2 class=\"firstH1\">Drip, Drip, Drip</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-202\" alt=\"Drip Drip Drip, photography\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/drip_drip_drip_ali_gray.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n<h2 class=\"paragraph\"><strong>Category:</strong> Photography</h2>\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2009\r\n\r\nI took this photo as part of a photography assignment for a university class, in which we had to find or create interesting text and letterforms and photograph them. I created and lit this scene in order to accomplish the look and concept I was after.\r\n<h2>China Shipping</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-200\" alt=\"China Shipping\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/china_shipping_ali_gray.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"574\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> Photography\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2012\r\n\r\nWhile out scouting for interesting typography and text to photograph for a typography class, I suddenly happened upon this fantastic truck parked in a downtown Missoula parking lot. What a great find!\r\n<h2>The Color of Rust</h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-205\" alt=\"The Color of Rust\" src=\"https://www