ton National Park. Went a little overboard with Photoshop, but I think the abstract-ness of the photo called for it.\r\n<h2>Color Wheel</h2>\r\n<img src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/circular_color_ali_gray.jpg\" alt=\"Color Wheel\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-712\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2010\r\n\r\nThis crayon tower had such amazing colors! Boosting said colors beyond the natural is always fun, as well.\r\n\r\n<h2>Pathways</h2>\r\n<img src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/pathways_ali_gray.jpg\" alt=\"Pathways\" width=\"800\" height=\"532\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-714\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2010\r\n\r\nCan you guess what this is? It\'s actually a quilt, transformed into a very three-dimensional looking image.\r\n\r\n<h2>Wavy</h2>\r\n<img src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/wavy_ali_gray.jpg\" alt=\"Wavy\" width=\"800\" height=\"257\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-747\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2014\r\n\r\nA wavy panorama of waves. iPhones can do fun things sometimes.\r\n\r\n<h2>Geometric</h2>\r\n<img src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/geometric_ali_gray.jpg\" alt=\"Geometric\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-745\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2014\r\n\r\nI love glass skyscrapers, and the way this one was reflecting itself in the twilight was perfect.\r\n\r\n<h2>A Point of Focus</h2>\r\n<img src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/a_point_of_focus_ali_gray.jpg\" alt=\"A Point of Focus\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-723\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2014\r\n\r\nI was going for getting more of the bus in focus, but I ended up liking this more abstract photo as the final choice.\r\n\r\n<hr>\r\n<p>I update this page frequently, so check back often to see my most recent photographs!</p>','Abstract Photography','','inherit','open','open','','732-revision-v1','','','2014-07-06 20:23:45','2014-07-07 02:23:45','',732,'https://www.iamalidesign.com/2014/07/06/732-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(755,1,'2014-07-07 20:34:27','2014-07-08 02:34:27','<h2 class=\"paragraph\"><strong>Category:</strong> Photography</h2>\r\n\r\n<h2 class=\"firstH1\">Drip, Drip, Drip</h2>\r\n<img src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/drip_drip_drip_ali_gray.jpg\" alt=\"Drip Drip Drip, photography\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-749\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2009\r\n\r\nI took this photo as part of a photography assignment for a university class, in which we had to find or create interesting text and letterforms and photograph them. I created and lit this scene in order to accomplish the look and concept I was after.\r\n<h2>China Shipping</h2>\r\n<img src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/china_shipping_ali_gray.jpg\" alt=\"China Shipping, photography\" width=\"800\" height=\"574\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-750\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2012\r\n\r\nWhile out scouting for interesting typography and text to photograph for a typography class, I suddenly happened upon this fantastic truck parked in a downtown Missoula parking lot. What a great find!\r\n<h2>The Color of Rust</h2>\r\n<img src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/the_color_of_rust_ali_gray.jpg\" alt=\"The Color of Rust\" width=\"500\" height=\"667\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-751\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2012\r\n\r\nIt\'s amazing what you can find among a bunch of old rusty mining equipment in the middle of an old field in the industrial sector of a Montana town.\r\n<h2>Million Dollar</h2>\r\n<img src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/million_dollar_ali_gray.jpg\" alt=\"Million Dollar\" width=\"500\" height=\"750\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-752\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2012\r\n\r\nAs I currently live in Jackson Hole, WY, I figured I might as well take a picture of the <a href=\"https://www.google.com/search?q=million+dollar+cowboy+bar&client=firefox-a&hs=eoD&rls=org.mozilla:en-US:official&channel=sb&source=lnms&tbm=isch&sa=X&ei=eZi5U8HTDM-myASIqYCwBg&ved=0CAoQ_AUoAw&biw=1540&bih=758#channel=sb&q=million%20dollar%20cowboy%20bar%20sign&revid=1985559828&rls=org.mozilla%3Aen-US%3Aofficial&tbm=isch&imgdii=_\" target=\"_blank\">famous bar</a> every one of the thousands of tourists take pictures of every day—but in a different way.\r\n<h2>Doble V</h2>\r\n<img src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/doble_v_ali_gray.jpg\" alt=\"Doble V\" width=\"500\" height=\"667\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-753\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2012\r\n\r\nFinding the right crop is what turning a boring apartment complex sign into something unique is all about.\r\n<h2>Symmetry</h2>\r\n<img src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/symmetry_ali_gray.jpg\" alt=\"Symmetry\" width=\"800\" height=\"629\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-754\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2012\r\n\r\nAnother interesting find for my typography photography assignment. Loved the symmetrical and asymmetrical aspects of the inside of this gazebo roof.\r\n\r\n<h2>225</h2>\r\n<img src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/doorway_ali_gray.jpg\" alt=\"Doorway\" width=\"500\" height=\"750\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-710\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Date:</strong> 2013\r\n\r\nAmazing door to one of the rooms at the Old Faithful Inn in Yellowstone.\r\n\r\n<hr>\r\n<p>I update this page frequently, so check back often to see my most recent photographs!</p>','Text Photography','Collection of my photographs featuring text & typography themes.','inherit','open','open','','199-revision-v1','','','2014-07-07 20:34:27','2014-07-08 02:34:27','',199,'https://www.