s for small businesses, creating logos and branding materials, and doing custom illustration for web or print. I also offer copywriting, editing, and photography services. I\'m fun-loving, imaginative, driven, and love what I do. I hope it shows.</strong>\n<h2>The long</h2>\nI grew up in Idaho, where I spent my days either in school or out in the wilderness skiing, hiking, or rafting all around the West. That or playing with our cats, dogs, horses, lizards, parakeets, ant farms... You get the picture.\n\nI cultivated a love for the arts (and cats) from my artist and ceramics teacher mom, and an interest in computers and how things work from my engineer dad (and later from my building teacher stepdad). I learned a love for the outdoors, the environment, and hard work from them all.\n\n[expand title=\"Read my full story\"]\n\nLater on, I moved to Montana to study Media Arts at the university in Missoula, and discovered my passion for design, illustration, and photography. And craft beer. And turned into an independent, feminist woman, as well as a conservation, animal rights, and political activist. All those great things college does for ya.\n\nWrenching myself away from the town I felt was home, I landed a job and moved to Jackson, Wyoming right after graduating. There, I became a professional web and graphic designer (but it didn\'t include a season ski pass – I\'m still bitter about that). I worked long hours, sat with big-wig clients, fine-tuned my skillset, and learned a ton.\n\nAfter feeling young and poor for a year and a half, I decided my personal life needed a boost and so moved to Portland, Oregon in late 2013, which has been my home ever since. In Portland, I\'ve met amazing people, worked at a wonderful job at Portland Community College as the sole web designer, and gotten to explore new places in the outdoors. I\'ve taken up ski mountaineering and climbing to add to my already full quiver of outdoor sports (and fill up my basement with gear). I\'ve met a wonderful partner, and made lasting friends. I\'ve continued to hone my design skills through work and freelance projects. I volunteer as a ski tour leader and publication content editor for our local climbing organization, and take my camera out every weekend. I cuddle with my kitty with a good book when it rains. What more can you ask for?\n\n[/expand]\n<h2 style=\"margin-top: 40px;\">I\'ve got the experience</h2>\n<div id=\"experience\">\n\n[col size=\"one_half\"]\n\n<strong>2008 - 2012</strong>\nBachelor of Arts in <a href=\"http://www.umt.edu/mediaarts/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Media Arts</a>\nThe University of Montana – Missoula, MT\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong>2011-2013</strong>\nWeb and graphic designer\n<a href=\"http://www.circ.biz/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Circ Design &amp; Media</a> – Jackson, WY\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong>2011 - 2012</strong>\nStudent web designer\n<a href=\"https://www.umt.edu/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">The University of Montana</a> – Missoula, MT\n\n[/col]\n\n[col size=\"one_half_last\"]\n\n<strong>2013-present</strong>\nWeb designer\n<a href=\"https://www.pcc.edu/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Portland Community College</a> – Portland, OR\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong>2018-present</strong>\nWriter and assistant content editor\n<a href=\"https://mazamas.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Mazamas</a> – Portland, OR\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong>Freelance</strong>\nGraphic and web design\nVarious clients – check out <a href=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/\">my portfolio</a>\n\n[/col]\n\n</div>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button\" href=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/ali-gray-resume.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Résumé</a></p>\n\n<h3>Proficiency</h3>\n[col size=\"one_third\"]\n<h4 style=\"font-size: 21px; text-align: center;\">UX / UI design</h4>\n[graph_lite id=\"1234\"]\n\n[/col]\n\n[col size=\"one_third\"]\n<h4 style=\"font-size: 21px; text-align: center;\">Front-end dev</h4>\n[graph_lite id=\"1236\"]\n\n[/col]\n\n[col size=\"one_third_last\"]\n<h4 style=\"font-size: 21px; text-align: center;\">Graphic design</h4>\n[graph_lite id=\"1237\"]\n\n[/col]\n\n[col size=\"one_third\"]\n<h4 style=\"font-size: 21px; text-align: center;\">Photography</h4>\n[graph_lite id=\"1238\"]\n\n[/col]\n\n[col size=\"one_third\"]\n<h4 style=\"font-size: 21px; text-align: center;\">Writing / Editing</h4>\n[graph_lite id=\"1239\"]\n\n[/col]\n\n[col size=\"one_third_last\"]\n<h4 style=\"font-size: 21px; text-align: center;\">Illustration</h4>\n[graph_lite id=\"1240\"]\n\n[/col]\n\n[col size=\"one_half\"]\n<h3>Preferences</h3>\n[xyz-ihs snippet=\"comparison\"]\n\n[/col]\n\n[col size=\"one_half_last\"]\n<h3>I...</h3>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Love to smile.</li>\n 	<li>Have a partner named Andy. He’s great.</li>\n 	<li>Am a crazy cat lady. My cat Kona is the best.</li>\n 	<li>Am a morning person.</li>\n 	<li>Am an environmentalist and animal rights activist.</li>\n 	<li>Am a skier, hiker, backpacker, photographer, writer, and wannabe mountain climber.</li>\n 	<li>Am a nasty liberal feminist.</li>\n 	<li>Enjoy coffee, sparkling water, and cold craft beer.</li>\n 	<li>Spend my free time reading, often biographies of badass outdoor women.</li>\n 	<li>Love being outside more than practically everything else.</li>\n 	<li>Don’t style my hair. Pretty much ever.</li>\n 	<li>Don\'t like celery, potatoes, or mustard – most other foods are game. Bread is my favorite.</li>\n</ul>\n[/col]\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button\" href=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/contact/\">Contact me</a></p>','About','','inherit','closed','closed','','20-autosave-v1','','','2019-08-17 14:07:15','2019-08-17 21:07:15','',20,'https://www.iamalidesign.com/2019/08/17/20-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1069,1,'2018-03-07 18:13:31','2018-03-08 02:13:31','[col size=\"one_half\"]\r\n\r\nLet\'s work together! &lt;br&gt;\r\nI\'d love to hear from you about project ideas. I\'m available for freelance work, and love working with others on larger projects.\r\n\r\n[/col]\r\n\r\n[col size=\"one_half_last\"][contact-form-7 id=\"998\" title=\"Contact Ali\"][/col]','Contact','','inherit','closed','closed','','997-revision-v1','','','2018-03-07 18:13:31','2018-03-08 02:13:31','',997,'https://www.iamalidesign.com/2018/03/07/997-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1001,1,'2018-02-22 09:21:09','2018-02-22 17:21:09',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','','1001','','','2018-02-22 09:21:09','2018-02-22 17:21:09','',0,'https://www.iamalidesign.com/2018/02/22/1001/',2,'nav_menu_item','',0),(1003,1,'2018-02-22 09:21:09','2018-02-22 17:21:09',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','','1003','','','2018-02-22 09:21:09','2018-02-22 17:21:09','',0,'https://www.iamalidesign.com/2018/02/22/1003/',3,'nav_menu_item','',0),(1004,1,'2018-02-22 09:21:09','2018-02-22 17:21:09',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','','1004','','','2018-02-22 09:21:09','2018-02-22 17:21:09','',0,'https://www.iamalidesign.com/2018/02/22/1004/',12,'nav_menu_item','',0),(1015,1,'2018-02-23 14:43:50','2018-02-23 22:43:50','[col size=\"one_half\"]\r\n\r\nHello! My name is <strong>Ali Gray</strong>, and I’m a designer currently residing in <strong>Portland, OR</strong>. I make things that not only <strong>look great</strong>, but <strong>solve problems</strong>, <strong>push creative boundaries</strong> and <strong>work in real world design</strong>.\r\n\r\n[/col]\r\n\r\n[col size=\"one_half_last\"]\r\n\r\nIn May 2012, I received a <strong>degree in Media Arts: Integrated Digital Media</strong> from the University of Montana in Missoula. While my degree focused mostly on motion design and animation, I have experience working as a web and graphic designer both at the <strong>university and professional levels</strong> since 2011. If you’d like to learn more, please download my <strong><a title=\"Resume\" href=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-con