sign-pink','','','2018-03-08 07:55:42','2018-03-08 15:55:42','',0,'https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/ski-topsheets/ali-gray-ski-design-pink.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1059,1,'2018-03-06 09:12:55','2018-03-06 17:12:55','','ali-gray-ski-design-teal','','inherit','open','closed','','ali-gray-ski-design-teal','','','2018-03-08 07:57:21','2018-03-08 15:57:21','',0,'https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/ski-topsheets/ali-gray-ski-design-teal.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1060,1,'2018-03-06 09:12:57','2018-03-06 17:12:57','','ali-gray-ski-design-white','<em>The more subdued chevron design, this design is made to calm the mind on those deep pow days • 2017</em>','inherit','open','closed','','ali-gray-ski-design-white','','','2018-03-08 07:57:03','2018-03-08 15:57:03','',0,'https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/ski-topsheets/ali-gray-ski-design-white.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1063,1,'2018-10-24 05:14:55','2018-10-24 12:14:55','[full_portfolio]\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_1058\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"1920\"]<img class=\"wp-image-1058 size-full\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/ski-topsheets/ali-gray-ski-design-pink.jpg\" alt=\"Ali Gray ski topsheet design pink, yellow, teal chevrons\" width=\"1920\" height=\"802\" /> <em><strong>Party Time</strong> • I rock this design on my personal skis, but it\'s really for all badass ladies out there • 2017</em>[/caption]\r\n\r\n[/full_portfolio]\r\n<h2>Ski topsheet designs</h2>\r\n[col size=\"one_half\" class=\"text-right portfolio-item-info\"]\r\n\r\n<strong>Category:</strong> <a href=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/portfolio-category/graphic-design/\">Graphic design</a>\r\n<strong>Client:</strong> <a href=\"https://maidenskis.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Maiden Skis</a>\r\n<strong>Year:</strong> 2013-present\r\n<strong>Press:</strong> <a href=\"https://maidenskis.com/blog/5-favorite-custom-skis-2017/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Maiden\'s 5 Favorite Custom Skis of 2017</a> | <a href=\"https://maidenskis.com/blog/3-reasons-consider-ski-urethane-sidewalls/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">3 Reasons to Consider a Ski with Urethane Sidewalls</a>\r\n\r\n[/col]\r\n\r\n[col size=\"one_half_last\"]\r\n\r\nI periodically do design work for Maiden Skis, a custom ski business out of Jackson Hole, WY. My topsheet designs are in use on various pairs of their skis (and a pair of my own!).\r\n\r\n[/col]\r\n<h3>Designed with stoke in mind</h3>\r\nI want my designs to be unique. We all strive to stand out on the slopes. With technology allowing us to go higher and faster every day, we need skis that show off, as well.\r\n\r\n[full_portfolio]\r\n\r\n[col size=\"one_third\"]\r\n<h4>Achieving my dreams</h4>\r\n<strong>Designing for skis has always been a fantasy of mine.</strong> I\'ve been an avid skier my entire life. I watched with disdain as the bright, crazy graphics of the 80s and 90s turned to boring blah during the 2000s. Snowboard graphic designers started having all the fun.\r\n\r\nLucky for us, during the last decade or so the ski design industry took off again. Now consumers can choose from a full lineup of amazing skis showcasing amazing artwork. <strong>I wanted in.</strong>\r\n\r\nI love the <strong>design challenge</strong> skis offer. Long and narrow is such an intriguing shape, and it\'s fun to brainstorm ideas that work with that extreme ratio. Plus, I enjoy getting creative with carrying the design across the divide between skis, or to mirror but not duplicate design elements.\r\n\r\nI\'ve only done a handful of ski topsheet designs so far, but hope to continue adding to my list in the years to come. It really has been a dream come true to meld my love of hitting the slopes and designing things for people to enjoy.\r\n\r\n[/col]\r\n\r\n[col size=\"two_third_last\"]\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_1052\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"3024\"]<img class=\"wp-image-1052 size-full\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/ski-topsheets/ali-gray-ski-topsheets-e1520465700924.jpg\" alt=\"Ali Gray Ski Topsheets design\" width=\"3024\" height=\"3558\" /> <em>Me the first time I took my new babies out to the mountain</em>[/caption]\r\n\r\n[/col]\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_1059\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"1920\"]<img class=\"wp-image-1059 size-full\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/ski-topsheets/ali-gray-ski-design-teal.jpg\" alt=\"Ali Gray ski topsheet design teal, red chevrons\" width=\"1920\" height=\"802\" /> <em><strong>The Natural</strong> • Designed to show off the ski\'s wood grain, this design works for anyone looking to stand out in a crowd • 2017</em>[/caption]\r\n\r\n[/full_portfolio]\r\n<h3>Some things I keep in mind when designing</h3>\r\n<blockquote>\"Ski and snowboard topsheets represent a unique challenge: The artwork won\'t remain static, or be on walls in museums, galleries or homes. Instead, the creative product heightens an athletic experience in a rugged, outdoor, always-changing natural environment.\" <cite>– Olivia Dwyer, REI Cop-Op Journal</cite></blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>[Do topsheets really sell skis?] \"Absolutely, no question about it.\" <cite>– Jed Duke, director of product for Blizzard Sport USA</cite></blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>\"Skis are a tough canvas. Long and skinny drawings can be hard to conceive. You have to funnel your creativity into a final project with lots of parameters and rules.\" <cite>– Lauren Bello, Coalition Snow Creative Director</cite></blockquote>\r\n[full_portfolio]\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_1060\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"1920\"]<img class=\"size-full wp-image-1060\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/ski-topsheets/ali-gray-ski-design-white.jpg\" alt=\"Ali Gray ski topsheet design white chevrons\" width=\"1920\" height=\"802\" /> <em><strong>Deep Pow</strong> • With a more subdued chevron design, this topsheet is made to calm the mind on those deep pow days • 2017</em>[/caption]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_913\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"900\"]<img class=\"wp-image-913 size-full\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/ski-graphics/ski-design1_ali-gray.jpg\" alt=\"Ali Gray ski topsheet design trees\" width=\"900\" height=\"1000\" /> <em><strong>Branch Out</strong> • I designed this ski with nature-loving shredders in mind • 2013</em>[/caption]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_1065\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"1920\"]<img class=\"size-full wp-image-1065\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/ski-topsheets/ali-gray-ski-design-retro.jpg\" alt=\"Ali Gray ski topsheet design retro geometric\" width=\"1920\" height=\"802\" /> <em><strong>The Retro</strong> • For those skiers stuck in the 80s • 2013</em>[/caption]\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h3>Recognition is always nice</h3>\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_1078\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"1416\"]<img class=\"size-full wp-image-1078\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/ski-topsheets/maiden-website.png\" alt=\"Maiden Skis website screenshot\" width=\"1416\" height=\"910\" /> <em>My designs featured on the Maiden Skis website</em>[/caption]\r\n\r\n[col size=\"one_half\"]\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1101\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/ski-topsheets/topsheets-blog1.png\" alt=\"Blog post 1\" width=\"1066\" height=\"880\" />\r\n\r\n[/col]\r\n\r\n[col size=\"one_half_last\"]\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1102\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/ski-topsheets/topsheets-blog2.png\" alt=\"Blog post 2\" width=\"1066\" height=\"880\" />\r\n\r\n[/col]\r\n\r\n[/full_portfolio]','Ski topsheets','','publish','closed','closed','','ski-topsheet-designs','','','2019-08-25 09:13:36','2019-08-25 16:13:36','',0,'https://www.iamalidesign.com/?po