ll wp-image-1065\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/ski-topsheets/ali-gray-ski-design-retro.jpg\" alt=\"Ali Gray ski topsheet design retro geometric\" width=\"1920\" height=\"802\" /> <em><strong>The Retro</strong> • For those skiers stuck in the 80s • 2013</em>[/caption]\n<h3></h3>\n<h3>Recognition is always nice</h3>\n[caption id=\"attachment_1078\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"1416\"]<img class=\"size-full wp-image-1078\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/ski-topsheets/maiden-website.png\" alt=\"Maiden Skis website screenshot\" width=\"1416\" height=\"910\" /> <em>My designs featured on the Maiden Skis website</em>[/caption]\n\n[col size=\"one_half\"]\n\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1101\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/ski-topsheets/topsheets-blog1.png\" alt=\"Blog post 1\" width=\"1066\" height=\"880\" />\n\n[/col]\n\n[col size=\"one_half_last\"]\n\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1102\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/ski-topsheets/topsheets-blog2.png\" alt=\"Blog post 2\" width=\"1066\" height=\"880\" />\n\n[/col]\n\n[/full_portfolio]','Ski Topsheets','','inherit','closed','closed','','1063-autosave-v1','','','2019-08-24 15:52:45','2019-08-24 22:52:45','',1063,'https://www.iamalidesign.com/2018/03/07/1063-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1068,1,'2018-03-07 18:11:57','2018-03-08 02:11:57','[col size=\"one_half\"]\r\n\r\nLet\'s work together! &lt;br&gt;\r\nI\'d love to hear from you.\r\n\r\n[/col]\r\n\r\n[col size=\"one_half_last\"][contact-form-7 id=\"998\" title=\"Contact Ali\"][/col]','Contact','','inherit','closed','closed','','997-revision-v1','','','2018-03-07 18:11:57','2018-03-08 02:11:57','',997,'https://www.iamalidesign.com/2018/03/07/997-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1070,1,'2018-03-07 18:14:01','2018-03-08 02:14:01','[col size=\"one_half\"]\r\n<h2>Let\'s work together!</h2>\r\nI\'d love to hear from you about project ideas. I\'m available