.com/portfolio-category/illustration/\">illustration</a>\r\n<strong>Client:</strong> <a href=\"https://www.portlandalpinefest.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Portland Alpine Festival</a> (unused design)\r\n<strong>Year:</strong> 2017\r\n\r\n[/col]\r\n\r\n[col size=\"one_half_last\"]\r\n\r\nThe designs on this page, which I entered into a logo design contest for the 2017 Portland Alpine Festival, show my train of thought for using related imagery in a variety of compositions.\r\n\r\n[/col]\r\n<h3>Climb (and design) on</h3>\r\nThe Portland Alpine Festival is a yearly event that <em>\"brings the community together for a series of clinics, seminars, and experiences that celebrate our shared interest in enjoying and preserving mountain environments.\"</em> From talks given by famous athletes to clinics introducing climbing or rescue skills, the event is for anyone interested in mountain recreation.\r\n<h4>To contest or not to contest</h4>\r\nI\'m apprehensive about entering design contests. They\'ve burned me in the past, and no one likes doing work for free. The whole concept can make it easy for designers to be taken advantage of. So when I saw an announcement about the PAF logo design content, my first instinct was a hard pass.\r\n\r\nBut then I thought about it, and figured that designing something that personally interests me seemed worthwhile, even if I was doing the work for free. I could have some fun. I volunteer regularly for the organization who puts on the festival, anyway.\r\n\r\nThe contest called for a logo to be used in a wide variety of places. The entered logo should be:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Full color for the PAF website, Mazamas website, and Mazama Bulletin magazine.</li>\r\n 	<li>Single color for the t-shirt, and for over the top of a photograph online or in print.</li>\r\n 	<li>Scalable for small and large use.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThe following concepts are what I came up with. My goal was to design something fun, inspired by vintage clothing tags or patches.\r\n<h3>Concept 1</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1206\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/paf-logo/paf1.png\" alt=\"PAF logo design 1\" width=\"1495\" height=\"768\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1210\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/paf-logo/paf-t-shirt.png\" alt=\"Concept 1 t-shirt\" width=\"900\" height=\"854\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1211\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/paf-logo/concept-1-magazine.png\" alt=\"Concept 1 magazine\" width=\"1000\" height=\"692\" />\r\n<h3>Concept 2</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1208\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/paf-logo/paf2.png\" alt=\"PAF logo design 2\" width=\"1495\" height=\"768\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1215\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/paf-logo/paf-t-shirt2.png\" alt=\"Concept 2 t-shirt\" width=\"900\" height=\"854\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1212\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/paf-logo/concept-2-magazine.png\" alt=\"Concept 2 magazine\" width=\"1000\" height=\"692\" />\r\n<h3>Concept 3</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1209\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/paf-logo/paf3.png\" alt=\"PAF logo design 3\" width=\"1495\" height=\"768\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1214\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/paf-logo/paf-t-shirt3.png\" alt=\"Concept 3 t-shirt\" width=\"900\" height=\"854\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1213\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/paf-logo/concept-3-magazine.png\" alt=\"Concept 3 magazine\" width=\"1000\" height=\"692\" />\r\n<h3>Concept 4</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1217\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/paf-logo/paf4.png\" alt=\"Other PAF concept\" width=\"1495\" height=\"768\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1256\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/paf-logo/paf-t-shirt4.png\" alt=\"Concept 4 t-shirt\" width=\"900\" height=\"854\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1255\" src=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/paf-logo/concept-4-magazine.png\" alt=\"Concept 4 magazine\" width=\"1000\" height=\"692\" />','Portland Alpine Festival','','publish','closed','closed','','paf-logos','','','2019-08-24 15:18:33','2019-08-24 22:18:33','',0,'https://www.iamalidesign.com/?post_type=portfolio&#038;p=1096',0,'portfolio','',0),(1097,1,'2018-03-19 16:19:56','2018-03-19 23:19:56','','paf-ali-gray-v1','','inherit','open','closed','','paf-ali-gray-v1','','','2018-03-19 16:21:20','2018-03-19 23:21:20','',1096,'https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/paf/paf-ali-gray-v1.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(1098,1,'2018-03-19 16:19:58','2018-03-19 23:19:58','','paf-ali-gray-v2','','inherit','open','closed','','paf-ali-gray-v2','','','2018-03-19 16:21:15','2018-03-19 23:21:15','',1096,'https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/paf/paf-ali-gray-v2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(1099,1,'2018-03-19 16:20:00','2018-03-19 23:20:00','','paf-ali-gray-v3','','inherit','open','closed','','paf-ali-gray-v3','','','2018-03-19 16:21:29','2018-03-19 23:21:29','',1096,'https://www.iamalidesign.com/wp-content/uploads/paf/paf-ali-gray-v3.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(1111,1,'2018-04-26 08:33:45','2018-04-26 15:33:45','[col size=\"one_half\"]\r\n\r\nHello! My name is <strong>Ali Gray</strong>, and I’m a designer currently residing in <strong>Portland, OR</strong>. I make things that not only <strong>look great</strong>, but <strong>solve problems</strong>, <strong>tell stories</strong>, and <strong>work in real world design</strong>.\r\n\r\n[/col]\r\n\r\n[col size=\"one_half_last\"]\r\n\r\nI\'ve been working profes