ion-4/',0,'visualizer','',0),(1172,1,'2018-10-18 13:28:46','2018-10-18 20:28:46','a:2:{i:0;a:2:{i:0;s:14:\"Graphic desgin\";i:1;d:65;}i:1;a:2:{i:0;s:4:\"none\";i:1;d:35;}}','Visualization','','publish','closed','closed','','visualization-3','','','2018-10-18 13:31:29','2018-10-18 20:31:29','',0,'https://www.iamalidesign.com/visualizer/visualization-3/',0,'visualizer','',0),(1175,1,'2018-10-18 13:31:29','2018-10-18 20:31:29','a:2:{i:0;a:2:{i:0;s:14:\"Graphic desgin\";i:1;d:65;}i:1;a:2:{i:0;s:4:\"none\";i:1;d:35;}}','Visualization','','inherit','closed','closed','','1172-revision-v1','','','2018-10-18 13:31:29','2018-10-18 20:31:29','',1172,'https://www.iamalidesign.com/2018/10/18/1172-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1230,1,'2019-05-10 14:34:04','2019-05-10 21:34:04','<h2>The short</h2>\r\n<strong>I\'m Ali, a web and graphic designer currently living in Portland, Oregon. I specialize in customizing WordPress themes for small businesses, creating logos and branding materials, and doing custom illustration for web or print. I also offer copywriting and photography services. I\'m fun-loving, imaginative, driven, and love what I do. I hope it shows.</strong>\r\n<h2>The long</h2>\r\nI grew up in Idaho, where I spent my days either in school or out in the wilderness skiing, hiking, or rafting all around the West. That or playing with our cats, dogs, horses, lizards, parakeets, ant farms... You get the picture.\r\n\r\nI cultivated a love for the arts (and cats) from my artist and ceramics teacher mom, and an interest in computers and how things work from my engineer dad (and later from my building teacher stepdad). I learned a love for the outdoors, the environment, and hard work from them all.\r\n\r\n[expand title=\"Read my full story\"]\r\n\r\nLater on, I moved to Montana to study Media Arts at the university in Missoula, and discovered my passion for design, illustration, and photography. And craft beer. And turned into an independent, feminist woman, as well as a conservation, animal rights, and political activist. All those great things college does for ya.\r\n\r\nWrenching myself away from the town I felt was home, I landed a job and moved to Jackson, Wyoming right after graduating. There, I became a professional web and graphic designer (but it didn\'t include a season ski pass – I\'m still bitter about that). I worked long hours, sat with big-wig clients, fine-tuned my skillset, and learned a ton.\r\n\r\nAfter feeling young and poor for a year and a half, I decided my personal life needed a boost and so moved to Portland, Oregon in late 2013, which has been my home ever since. In Portland, I\'ve met amazing people, worked at a wonderful job at Portland Community College as the sole web designer, and gotten to explore new places in the outdoors. I\'ve taken up ski mountaineering and climbing to add to my already full quiver of outdoor sports (and fill up my basement with gear). I\'ve met a wonderful partner, and made lasting friends. I\'ve continued to hone my design skills through work and freelance projects. I volunteer as a ski tour leader and publication content editor for our local climbing organization, and take my camera out every weekend. I cuddle with my kitty with a good book when it rains. What more can you ask for?\r\n\r\n[/expand]\r\n<h2 style=\"margin-top: 40px;\">I\'ve got the experience</h2>\r\n<div id=\"experience\">\r\n\r\n[col size=\"one_half\"]\r\n\r\n<strong>2008 - 2012</strong>\r\nBachelor of Arts in <a href=\"http://www.umt.edu/mediaarts/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Media Arts</a>\r\nThe University of Montana – Missoula, MT\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>2013-present</strong>\r\nWeb designer\r\n<a href=\"https://www.pcc.edu/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Portland Community College</a> – Portland, OR\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>2011-2013</strong>\r\nWeb and graphic designer\r\n<a href=\"http://www.circ.biz/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Circ Design &amp; Media</a> – Jackson, WY\r\n\r\n[/col]\r\n\r\n[col size=\"one_half_last\"]\r\n\r\n<strong>2011 - 2012</strong>\r\nStudent web designer\r\n<a href=\"https://www.umt.edu/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">The University of Montana</a> – Missoula, MT\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>2011</strong>\r\nStudent web content manager\r\n<a href=\"http://www.umt.edu/mediaarts/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">UM Media Arts</a> + <a href=\"http://www.umt.edu/creativepulse/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Creative Pulse</a> – Missoula, MT\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Freelance</strong>\r\nGraphic and web design\r\nVarious clients – check out <a href=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/\">my portfolio</a>\r\n\r\n[/col]\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>Proficiency</h3>\r\n[col size=\"one_third\"]\r\n<h4 style=\"font-size: 21px; text-align: center;\">UX / UI design</h4>\r\n[visualizer id=\"1163\"]\r\n\r\n[/col]\r\n\r\n[col size=\"one_third\"]\r\n<h4 style=\"font-size: 21px; text-align: center;\">Front-end dev</h4>\r\n[visualizer id=\"1226\"]\r\n\r\n[/col]\r\n\r\n[col size=\"one_third_last\"]\r\n<h4 style=\"font-size: 21px; text-align: center;\">Graphic design</h4>\r\n[visualizer id=\"1172\"]\r\n\r\n[/col]\r\n\r\n[col size=\"one_third\"]\r\n<h4 style=\"font-size: 21px; text-align: center;\">Photography</h4>\r\n[visualizer id=\"1178\"]\r\n\r\n[/col]\r\n\r\n[col size=\"one_third\"]\r\n<h4 style=\"font-size: 21px; text-align: center;\">Copywriting</h4>\r\n[visualizer id=\"1184\"]\r\n\r\n[/col]\r\n\r\n[col size=\"one_third_last\"]\r\n<h4 style=\"font-size: 21px; text-align: center;\">Illustration</h4>\r\n[visualizer id=\"1188\"]\r\n\r\n[/col]\r\n\r\n[col size=\"one_half\"]\r\n<h3>Preferences</h3>\r\n[xyz-ihs snippet=\"comparison\"]\r\n\r\n[/col]\r\n\r\n[col size=\"one_half_last\"]\r\n<h3>I...</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Have a partner named Andy. He’s great.</li>\r\n 	<li>Am a crazy cat lady – my cat Kona is the best.</li>\r\n 	<li>Am a morning person.</li>\r\n 	<li>Am an environmentalist and animal rights activist.</li>\r\n 	<li>Am a skier, hiker, camper, backpacker, photographer, and wannabe mountain climber.</li>\r\n 	<li>Am a nasty liberal feminist.</li>\r\n 	<li>Enjoy coffee, water, and cold craft beer.</li>\r\n 	<li>Spend my free time reading, often biographies of badass outdoor women.</li>\r\n 	<li>Love being outside more than practically everything else.</li>\r\n 	<li>Don’t style my hair. Pretty much ever.</li>\r\n 	<li>Don\'t like celery, potatoes, or mustard – most other foods are game. Bread is my favorite.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/col]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button\" href=\"https://www.iamalidesign.com/contact/\">Contact me</a></p>','About','','inherit','closed','closed','','20-revision-v1','','','2019-05-10 14:34:04','2019-05-10 21:34:04','',20,'https://www.iamalidesign.com/2019/05/10/20-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1184,1,'2018-10-18 13:53:44','2018-10-18 20:53:44','a:2:{i:0;a:2:{i:0;s:11:\"Copywriting\";i:1;d:75;}i:1;a:2:{i:0;s:4:\"none\";i:1;d:25;}}','Visualization','','publish','closed','closed','','visualization-5','','','2018-10-18 13:54:51','2018-10-18 20:54:51','',0,'https://www.iamalidesign.com/visualizer/visualization-5/',0,'visualizer','',0),(1188,1,'2018-10-18 13:55:47','2018-10-18 20:55:47','a:2:{i:0;a:2:{i:0;s:12:\"Illustration\";i:1;d:40;}i:1;a:2:{i:0;s:4:\"none\";i:1;d:60;}}','Visualization','','publish','closed','closed','','visualization-6','','','2018-10-18 13:56:46','2018-10-18 20:56:46','',0,'https://www.iamalidesign.com/visualizer/visualization-6/',0,'visualizer','',0),(1187,1,'2018-10-18 13:54:51','2018-10-18 20:54:51','a:2:{i:0;a:2:{i:0;s:11:\"Copywriting\";i:1;d:75;}i:1;a:2:{i:0;s:4:\"none\";i:1;d:25;}}','Visualization','','inherit','closed','closed','','1184-revision-v1','','','2018-10-18 13:54:51','2018-10-18 20:54:51','',1184,'https://www.iamalidesign.com/2018/10/18/1184-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1197,1,'2018-10-18 14:32:51','2018-10-18 21:32:51','<h2>The short</h2>\r\n<strong>I\'m Ali, a web and graphic designer current